{"tid":1847720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話你知「行動逼使封關」同「請願等待政府封關」嘅下場分別","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T11:19:49.000Z","uid":131691,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"29d8c145787952d4ee30c5d5fb67d86cce5841d1","tid":1847720,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"情景一：<br />\n香港人以罷工，阻路，炸關口等等積極行動逼使封關<br />\n結果：<br />\n香港人成功保衛家園，截堵外來入侵者<br />\n香港人證明俾全世界睇，控制香港邊疆嘅權力係屬於香港人嘅<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">簡稱：香港人宣示香港領土主權</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情景二：<br />\n香港人以請願，遞信，等民建聯協商等等消極方式等待政府封關<br />\n結果：<br />\n在中共政府英明嘅領導下，香港得救<br />\n親中派成功爭取封關<br />\n老泛民，大中華膠及律師黨表示「中国仍未放棄香港，一國兩制有險可守」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>歷史書將會記錄：中国成功由美國製造嘅瘟疫中救咗屬於中国嘅香港</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b25c3b937a074dd813bf86537868be542f41733a","tid":1847720,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:30:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c56c2fc962c9d37cf6ad3d8abbeba3f5f5cd5368","tid":1847720,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"問題係請願完都唔會封"},{"pid":"d0fd9793352de106c2737b87ccc2cf8288e9dfd3","tid":1847720,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c56c2fc962c9d37cf6ad3d8abbeba3f5f5cd5368","tid":1847720,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"問題係請願完都唔會封"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"但係都唔可以俾呢個歷史嘅可能存在"},{"pid":"19ed70dd03ca9f1acc0adc27c3d5610e333b88b1","tid":1847720,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebe688d4e29db26dd6662a3e062233b60a10105","tid":1847720,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割唔係口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fef4b938412af7697d9b449b7fd4aba8f32165","tid":1847720,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:47:11.000Z","msg":"沒有主權，何來抗疫？<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b52f74c219a3b1e1eff86d0e0a69abbaf6b7e6","tid":1847720,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"係，就係咁"},{"pid":"4c9b12134a2a82c957f3c382237d46c0a9f69b33","tid":1847720,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"好記得高學歷廢青好耐以前分享過唔同嘅stage<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政治動盪期後，殖民者就會走出嚟扮好人，全面统治香港"